description: This file defines a function 'generateStaticParams' for use in a Next.js application to determine static parameters for dynamic routes. Specifically, it provides static route parameters for pages that are pre-rendered, with the current implementation returning an empty array indicating no pages to pre-render at build time.

methods.name: export function generateStaticParams(): Array<{ id: string }> { generateStaticParams
methods.description: Returns an array of route parameter objects for static site generation, specifically for the notes editing pages. Currently returns an empty array to skip pre-rendering these pages at build time.
